263
00:15:36,719 --> 00:15:39,760
It is defined in relation to fares

264
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:43,282
and the ability to access for a large number of citizens

265
00:15:43,282 --> 00:15:46,173
from different social backgrounds.

266
00:15:46,173 --> 00:15:51,074
This is especially important as the production of public transport

267
00:15:51,074 --> 00:15:54,947
is often marked by social prism or even socio-economic

268
00:15:54,947 --> 00:15:57,620
which aims to link neighborhoods together

269
00:15:57,620 --> 00:16:02,351
and to create diversity by bringing jobs to people.

270
00:16:02,881 --> 00:16:06,076
So that citizens can use the offer

271
00:16:06,076 --> 00:16:08,428
they should simply be able to

272
00:16:08,428 --> 00:16:11,544
afford to buy a ticket.

273
00:16:12,724 --> 00:16:15,029
The last point concerns security.

274
00:16:15,708 --> 00:16:19,260
It goes through a series of technical devices but also human

275
00:16:19,260 --> 00:16:23,042
for citizens to use public transport offered

276
00:16:23,042 --> 00:16:26,216
they should have above all a sense of security

277
00:16:26,216 --> 00:16:29,365
which allows them to borrow this transport without fear.

278
00:16:29,933 --> 00:16:35,760
This involves safety of users compared to physical attacks,

279
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:38,001
thefts and accidents.

280
00:16:39,088 --> 00:16:42,024
It can go through a series of devices

281
00:16:42,083 --> 00:16:46,085
who are lighting stations or the installation of safety barriers,

282
00:16:46,296 --> 00:16:47,859
awareness,

283
00:16:47,859 --> 00:16:51,700
conflict mediation, control of ticket

284
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:54,771
or extreme police repression.

285
00:16:56,027 --> 00:16:58,456
The adhesion in terms of organizational processes

286
00:16:58,456 --> 00:17:00,164
and sets of actors in turn

287
00:17:00,164 --> 00:17:04,940
involves initially the idea that territorial producers actors

288
00:17:04,944 --> 00:17:07,731
adhere to the proposed transportation project

289
00:17:07,731 --> 00:17:11,679
and integrate the processes and dynamics at work or in the future.

290
00:17:13,038 --> 00:17:16,570
Secondly, this implies that the project itself

