00:17:16,570 --> 00:17:20,775
integrates the dynamics of various actors in its own process.

292
00:17:21,521 --> 00:17:24,891
As dynamic participating in the manufacture of the city,

293
00:17:24,911 --> 00:17:26,462
the creation, the management

294
00:17:26,462 --> 00:17:29,606
or the reorganization of a system or mode of transport

295
00:17:29,606 --> 00:17:32,040
systematically creates an interaction

296
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:34,736
with other city productive dynamics.

297
00:17:35,201 --> 00:17:38,144
It highlights interaction of public sector actors

298
00:17:38,144 --> 00:17:40,202
private sector actors

299
00:17:40,202 --> 00:17:42,441
and civil society.

300
00:17:42,441 --> 00:17:44,198
It also uses interaction

301
00:17:44,198 --> 00:17:46,737
between different territorial scales levels

302
00:17:46,737 --> 00:17:51,192
that correspond to a variety of actors and systems of organizations

303
00:17:51,192 --> 00:17:55,544
and territorial production processes just as different.

304
00:17:56,261 --> 00:18:00,271
The adherence of this level of transport is its ability to hold

305
00:18:00,271 --> 00:18:02,767
the processes at work in the territory

306
00:18:03,099 --> 00:18:06,358
and integrate the demands and plans of the various actors.

307
00:18:07,285 --> 00:18:11,020
It is also its ability to adhere to different territorial levels

308
00:18:11,020 --> 00:18:16,325
and integrate into the overall process the processed that involve each scale.

309
00:18:17,105 --> 00:18:19,925
This adherence of organizational processes

310
00:18:19,925 --> 00:18:22,822
and territorial actors is not only concerned

311
00:18:22,822 --> 00:18:25,617
by the duration of the project until its completion.

312
00:18:25,617 --> 00:18:27,065
The city changes.

313
00:18:27,065 --> 00:18:28,894
It is constantly changing.

314
00:18:29,249 --> 00:18:32,425
Its games of actors and production dynamics are

315
00:18:32,425 --> 00:18:35,427
in perpetual motion and reconfiguration.

